      "description": "Available is an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54B32 inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox, providing tactile engagement and precise shift gates. The mechanical integrity is superlative, having undergone a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and proactive rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity. The factory Variable M Differential Lock operates flawlessly, delivering optimal torque distribution. With zero bushing deflection and a pristine underside, this specimen represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated M-division engineering, offered in turn-key, showroom condition.",
